title: New Note, My Cats
text:
This is my notes app. 
I use this mostly to take notes about my cats and their health. 
I have 5 cats and they are a handful. 
Their daily habits are a lot to keep track of so this will help me keep things organized all in one place! 

Notes app! Hurray!
